        <div class="mb-2">
            <p>There are several major reasons why a school websites would be incredibly benefital; and this are some of he major reasons;</p>
            <p>Does your school really need website development and how will it benefit from such a project? A personalized, functional website will result in reputation establishment possibilities that will be unavailable through any other channel. </p>
            <p> It is easy to neglect your school website, but this would be a big mistake. Your website can accomplish so much for your school, your staff and your whole community. A website needs to not only look good and provide the basic information – it should also become an interactive hub for the community.</p>
        </div>
